title 主流程活动图
start
:进入 buildRecommendations();
:resolveTimingPresetConfig();
:建立 positionsByCode + remainingRiskBudget;
:遍历 timingCards 生成 Candidate;
:normalizeForMarket();
:PositionContextService.build();
:normalizeForPosition();
:getSuggestedRange();
:adjustConfidence() + computeScore();
:按 score 降序排序;
:按 remainingRiskBudget 截断或 downgrade;
:重算 positionContext(targetDeltaPct);
:组装 TimingRecommendationDraft.reasoning;
:返回 recommendations;
stop
